entries.title: Are You Switching to a Heat Pump? We Want to Hear From You.
entries.description: Some people in extremely cold areas of the U.S. are switching to heat pumps from oil or gas furnaces. But others are not convinced that these devices are right for them.

entries.title: Advisory Firm Sues Elon Musk’s Twitter, Saying It Hasn’t Been Paid
entries.description: Innisfree M&A says Twitter, which Elon Musk bought last year, has not paid it $1.9 million for services it rendered for the deal.
